		</a><br>
		<div class="text">
			<p>We love the range of topics on HubPages. We go deep and we go wide (sometimes we even get lost in our Hubs). We&rsquo;re passionate about discovering and sharing information. And about creating a community. In a very real sense, we&rsquo;re in this to make an impact, to grow, to learn, to share knowledge, to connect to each other and to something bigger. We get excited by our company, by our Hubbers&mdash;every day. We&rsquo;re in it to change the world, in our own small way.</p>
		</div>
